title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 7
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. The longest podcast of the season and action packed with drama. Rico may have had oblos and missed the 3:30 SEC game. Plus a potential new podcast on the horizon??


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
